description: The Invisible Man (1897) is one of the most gripping of H.G. Wells' science-fiction sagas. The Invisible Man is the story of a brilliant young scientist who hastily experiments upon himself, becoming invisible and mad. He is imprisoned in a nightmare of his own making. From its opening in a small village inn, the narrative moves inexorably towards a climax of terror as the whole of England unites to hunt down and destroy the invisible alien. Beautifully illustrated, this classic tale captures the imagination of readers of all ages and inspires a love of literature and reading.
name: The Invisible Man

deck: An anthology of tales featuring an invasion of stone men from deep within the Earth.
description:
Features Include:

  1. I Saw The Invasion Of The Stone Men! - (Ditko) giant stone men emerge in the heart of New York City. One scientist thinks he knows why, but no one will listen to him!
  2. Patent Pending - (unknown) text story about a young inventor who experiences strange encounters when he's close to completing a prototype.
  3. I was the Man Under Glass! - (unknown) An arrogant colonial governor of an alien planet meets a fate of his own making.
  4. I Laughed at the Great God Pan - (unknown) while visiting a museum a young couple hears the story of Pan.
  5. I Became a Human Bomb! - (Reinman) a small time hood plans to steal an Air Force missile.
  6. I Was Prisoner of the Living Statues! - (Forte) aliens invade a small village in Africa
name: I Saw The Invasion Of The Stone Men!

description:
Challenge of the Weather Wizard!

Never in the cyclonic career of mighty Flash has the World's Fastest Human met anyone quite like the bizarre villain who tamed the atmosphere and made it sit and do tricks! In fact the Scarlet Speedster himself needs every super-speed trick up his sleeve in order to meet--"The challenge of the Weather Wizard!"

Meet Kid Flash!

Barry Allen, alias The Flash, thought that he alone in the world possessed the gift of super-speed! And Barry's belief was correct--until one momentous day when an incredible accident happened--an accident that resulted in the appearance of a startling new figure in the continuous combat against evil and injustice! "Meet Kid Flash!"
name: Challenge of the Weather Wizard! / Meet Kid Flash!
